name: End Israeli Apartheid (Proceeds to MAPs)
description: @DolCreative - Created using lino printing, spray paint, and acrylic paint, this piece is a call to end apartheid taking place in Israel against the people of Palestine. All profits raised from the sale of this token will be donated to Medical Aid for Palestinians. MAPs are on the ground in Gaza, the West Bank, and Lebanon providing emergency frontline health services to those in the greatest need. Lets make NFTs a force for good.
